{"tid":2029638,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國安法有幾嚴? 可以睇下零八憲章, 足以令劉曉波被判死刑+全家被搞","createTime":"2020-05-22T10:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T02:06:12.000Z","uid":19552,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"58904aacc8515eb3f9b13912864373dd3b37e5c3","tid":2029638,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:29:18.000Z","msg":"基本理念<br />\n自由：言論、出版、信仰、集會、結社、遷徙、罷工和遊行示威等權利。<br />\n人權：人是國家的主體，國服務於人民，政府為人民而存在。<br />\n平等：公民不論社會地位、職業、性別、經濟狀況、種族、膚色、宗教或政治信仰，其人格、尊嚴、自由都是平等的。<br />\n共和：要求「大家共治，和平共生」，分權制衡與利益平衡。<br />\n民主：主權在民和民選政府。<br />\n憲政：主張以法治限制政府權力和行為的邊界。<br />\n<br />\n《零八憲章》內容觸及政治改革、經濟改革、城鄉差距與環境保護等諸多方面，並提出十九點基本主張包括：<br />\n修改憲法<br />\n分權制衡<br />\n立法民主<br />\n司法獨立<br />\n公器公用<br />\n人權保障<br />\n公職選舉<br />\n城鄉平等<br />\n結社自由<br />\n集會自由<br />\n言論自由<br />\n宗教自由<br />\n公民教育<br />\n財產保護<br />\n財稅改革"},{"pid":"f32572f73d51d160e0787913688ac4cbe8c6d3ed","tid":2029638,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:30:32.000Z","msg":"拜拜👋"},{"pid":"3faa55ff1a7e97ca5d4676dd9d430d17bcf2207c","tid":2029638,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e391375aa6e186d6e06a58223d0bebe20c977c","tid":2029638,"uid":83344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:30:44.000Z","msg":"國安法下有言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1392556dc85d7fb7631a60fd6e2ca9653b11030","tid":2029638,"uid":34235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:31:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"